<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Spectres FTIR — Visualisation & Comparaisons</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,300;9..144,400;9..144,600;9..144,800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.0/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0e1014;
    --surface: #161a21;
    --surface-2: #1d222b;
    --border: #2a313d;
    --text: #e8ecf2;
    --text-dim: #8a93a3;
    --accent: #d4a857;
    --c1: #6ec1e4;   /* spectre 1 */
    --c2: #f08a5d;   /* spectre 2 */
    --c3: #b8e0a0;   /* spectre 3 - référence */
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html, body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  body {
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(212,168,87,0.08), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 100% 100%, rgba(110,193,228,0.05), transparent 60%);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  header {
    padding: 56px 48px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .subtitle {
    margin-top: 14px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 16px;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  main {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 48px 80px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 56px;
  }

  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 18px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .section-num {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .section-desc {
    margin-left: auto;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  .grid-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 20px 22px 16px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .swatch {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 17px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .card-meta {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .chart-wrap {
    position: relative;
    height: 280px;
  }
  .chart-wrap-large {
    position: relative;
    height: 480px;
  }

  .stats-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding-top: 12px;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--border);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .stat-val {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .legend-line {
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .controls {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn {
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  .btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .btn.active {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #1a1a1a;
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  footer {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px 48px 48px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="eyebrow">FTIR · Analyse spectrale · 26·04·2020</div>
  <h1>Trois spectres infrarouges,<br><em>deux comparaisons.</em></h1>
  <p class="subtitle">
    Visualisation individuelle de chaque spectre, suivie de comparaisons superposées
    (Spectre 1 vs 3, puis Spectre 2 vs 3) pour mettre en évidence les bandes communes
    et les différences caractéristiques.
  </p>
</header>

<main>

  <!-- SECTION 1 : SPECTRES INDIVIDUELS -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-num">01</span>
      <span class="section-title">Spectres individuels</span>
      <span class="section-desc">399 — 4000 cm⁻¹ · 3736 points</span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <span class="swatch" style="background: var(--c1)"></span>
          <span class="card-title">Spectre 1</span>
          <span class="card-meta">01aa</span>
        </div>
        <div class="chart-wrap"><canvas id="ch1"></canvas></div>
        <div class="stats-row" id="stats1"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <span class="swatch" style="background: var(--c2)"></span>
          <span class="card-title">Spectre 2</span>
          <span class="card-meta">02</span>
        </div>
        <div class="chart-wrap"><canvas id="ch2"></canvas></div>
        <div class="stats-row" id="stats2"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <span class="swatch" style="background: var(--c3)"></span>
          <span class="card-title">Spectre 3</span>
          <span class="card-meta">caf · réf.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="chart-wrap"><canvas id="ch3"></canvas></div>
        <div class="stats-row" id="stats3"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2 : COMPARAISON 1 vs 3 -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-num">02</span>
      <span class="section-title">Spectre 1 &nbsp;vs&nbsp; Spectre 3</span>
      <span class="section-desc">superposition</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="legend">
        <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-line" style="background: var(--c1)"></span>Spectre 1 (01aa)</div>
        <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-line" style="background: var(--c3)"></span>Spectre 3 (caf · référence)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="controls">
        <button class="btn active" data-target="cmp13" data-range="full">Plage complète</button>
        <button class="btn" data-target="cmp13" data-range="finger">Empreinte (400–1500)</button>
        <button class="btn" data-target="cmp13" data-range="mid">Moyen (1500–2500)</button>
        <button class="btn" data-target="cmp13" data-range="oh">O-H / C-H (2500–4000)</button>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-wrap-large"><canvas id="cmp13"></canvas></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3 : COMPARAISON 2 vs 3 -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-num">03</span>
      <span class="section-title">Spectre 2 &nbsp;vs&nbsp; Spectre 3</span>
      <span class="section-desc">superposition</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="legend">
        <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-line" style="background: var(--c2)"></span>Spectre 2 (02)</div>
        <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-line" style="background: var(--c3)"></span>Spectre 3 (caf · référence)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="controls">
        <button class="btn active" data-target="cmp23" data-range="full">Plage complète</button>
        <button class="btn" data-target="cmp23" data-range="finger">Empreinte (400–1500)</button>
        <button class="btn" data-target="cmp23" data-range="mid">Moyen (1500–2500)</button>
        <button class="btn" data-target="cmp23" data-range="oh">O-H / C-H (2500–4000)</button>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-wrap-large"><canvas id="cmp23"></canvas></div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<footer>
  Données : JASCO · Transmittance (%) vs Nombre d'onde (cm⁻¹) · Survolez les courbes pour les valeurs précises.
</footer>

